If you ever need a reminder of
the syntax of any of these statements,

00:04:07.610 --> 00:04:11.060
you can just check the official
Java documentation.

00:04:11.060 --> 00:04:14.240
It tells you about the if statement,
and here's an example.

00:04:15.540 --> 00:04:19.560
And then it also shows you that if
else statement and here's the example.

